<main class="w-full">
  <div class="relative flex justify-center items-center min-h-screen text-white w-full bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511300636408-a63a89df3482?q=80&w=1470&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fA%3D%3D')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat">

    <section class="flex">
      <div class="h-auto w-3/4 md:w-2/3 lg:w-2/3 xl:max-w-screen-xl items-center flex flex-col">
        <section id="timer" class="text-center select-none">
          <div data-controller="countdown" data-action="settings:changed@window->countdown#applySettings">
            <%= render 'top_navigation' %>
            <%= render 'timer' %>
            <%= render 'bottom_navigation' %>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50">
      <%= render 'settings_button' %>
    </div>
    <div>

    <%= render 'settings_modal' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
<!--
- Focus bg selected by default  ✅

When focus timer goes down -> change to short break and change the number of cycles +1  ✅
When break timer goes down -> change to focus add number of breaks(total) to localStorage  ✅
On every %4 === 0  loop Instead of changing to ShortBreak move to Long Break  ✅

Settings
Panel to Change Focus, Short Break, Long break Duration (save to localStorage)✅
Panel to Change number of loops before going to Long Break✅
sidebar ->
  - button to log in // optional
  - button to select sound
  - button to select bg


Notification when either timer goes down (sound)

-->